<body>

<div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">

        <h1>Privacy Policy - Melody Rush (MR)</h1>

        <p class="date">
            Last updated: May 22, 2026
        </p>

        <p>
            This Privacy Policy explains how <strong>Melody Rush (MR)</strong>
            collects, uses, stores, and protects user information.
        </p>

        <p>
            By using the game, you agree to the practices described in this policy.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

        <p>
            Melody Rush (MR) does not directly collect personally identifiable
            information such as:
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Full names</li>
            <li>Addresses</li>
            <li>Phone numbers</li>
            <li>Passwords</li>
            <li>Personal photographs</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            However, integrated third-party services required for gameplay
            functionality may process limited technical or gameplay-related information.
        </p>

        <p>This information may include:</p>

        <ul>
            <li>Device information</li>
            <li>Operating system version</li>
            <li>Crash logs and diagnostics</li>
            <li>Gameplay progress and save data</li>
            <li>Country or region</li>
            <li>Anonymous identifiers required for cloud saving and account persistence</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. Third-Party Services</h2>

        <p>
            Melody Rush (MR) may use trusted third-party services to support
            gameplay functionality, cloud saving, and in-app purchases.
        </p>

        <p>These services may include:</p>

        <ul>
            <li>PlayFab (cloud save and online functionality)</li>
            <li>Google Play Services</li>
            <li>Unity Gaming Services</li>
            <li>Unity In-App Purchasing (IAP)</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            These providers may process technical information necessary
            for the game to function correctly.
        </p>

        <h2>3. How Information Is Used</h2>

        <p>Information may be used to:</p>

        <ul>
            <li>Save player progress</li>
            <li>Provide online functionality</li>
            <li>Restore cloud save data</li>
            <li>Improve game stability and performance</li>
            <li>Fix bugs and crashes</li>
            <li>Verify in-app purchases</li>
            <li>Prevent abuse or fraudulent activity</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="account-deletion">4. Account and Data Deletion</h2>

        <div class="notice">
            <strong>Melody Rush (MR) allows users to delete their account and associated gameplay data.</strong>
        </div>

        <h3>Delete your account inside the game</h3>

        <p>
            Users can permanently delete their account and associated data
            directly within the game.
        </p>

        <div class="steps">
            <strong>Steps:</strong>
            <ol>
                <li>Open Melody Rush (MR)</li>
                <li>Go to <strong>Settings</strong></li>
                <li>Open <strong>Account</strong></li>
                <li>Select <strong>Delete Account</strong></li>
                <li>Confirm deletion</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <p>
            Account deletion may permanently remove:
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Game progress</li>
            <li>Cloud save data</li>
            <li>Associated gameplay information</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Need help deleting your account?</h3>

        <p>
            If you cannot access the in-game deletion option,
            you may request account or data deletion by contacting:
        </p>

        <p>
            <span class="email">thegolmusicgame@gmail.com</span>
        </p>

        <p>
            Email subject:
            <strong>Melody Rush Account Deletion Request</strong>
        </p>

        <p>
            Requests are typically processed within
            <strong>7 business days</strong>.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>

        <p>
            Melody Rush (MR) is not intentionally directed toward children
            below the minimum age required under applicable local laws.
        </p>

        <p>
            We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Data Security</h2>

        <p>
            Reasonable measures are taken to protect information handled
            through trusted third-party services. However, no online
            service can guarantee complete security.
        </p>

        <h2>7. External Links</h2>

        <p>
            The game may contain links to third-party websites or services.
            We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices
            of external websites.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>

        <p>
            This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically.
            Any changes will be reflected on this page together with
            an updated revision date.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Contact</h2>

        <p>
            If you have questions regarding this Privacy Policy,
            your account, or your data, contact:
        </p>

        <p>
            <span class="email">thegolmusicgame@gmail.com</span>
        </p>

        <footer>
            Melody Rush (MR) © 2026
        </footer>

